  "title": "Project Manager (Construction / HDB Projects)",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Construction industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Project Manager </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> Project Manager</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Central (Nearest MRT: Mattar)</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 5.5 days, Office Hours</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $10,000 + Bonus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead project planning and execution, ensuring all activities are accurately prepared and carried out to meet project objectives.</li>\n  <li>Serve as the primary point of contact for all project stakeholders, including clients, consultants, regulatory bodies, and subcontractors, to ensure seamless project progression.</li>\n  <li>Develop, review, and submit comprehensive project documentation, including detailed programs, schedules, method statements, technical proposals, and risk assessments.</li>\n  <li>Conduct regular safety and progress meetings with internal teams, subcontractors, and on-site personnel to maintain high safety and performance standards.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least a Diploma in Civil Engineering, Construction Management or other related discipline.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 5 years of experience working in the construction industry, with experience in handling HDB projects.</li>\n  <li>Must be capable of leading and managing a project team.</li>\n  <li>Able to work in a fast paced environment and under tight deadlines.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to<strong> </strong><a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
